No, don't do it.

954
00:39:08,288 --> 00:39:09,700
- All done.
- You already transferred?

955
00:39:09,700 --> 00:39:11,560
If your mom finds out, she's going to...

956
00:39:12,810 --> 00:39:13,930
I helped you hide it in this.

957
