Look, this is the "Wealth Manager" app.

958
00:39:17,511 --> 00:39:19,177
Mom doesn't know about this thing.

959
00:39:19,755 --> 00:39:20,800
She doesn't know it.

960
00:39:20,822 --> 00:39:22,377
I don't know how to use it either.

961
00:39:22,466 --> 00:39:24,000
All you have to do is transfer it out

962
00:39:24,160 --> 00:39:25,560
when you need it.

963
00:39:27,080 --> 00:39:27,760
Wait, I thought

964
00:39:28,010 --> 00:39:29,760
Shen Qing still needed some money too?

965
00:39:30,490 --> 00:39:32,240
You two are quite tight in cash too.

966
00:39:32,466 --> 00:39:33,800
This amount doesn't affect much.

967
00:39:34,490 --> 00:39:35,280
I made this money

968
00:39:35,680 --> 00:39:37,240
and I want to spend it on you.

969
00:39:40,010 --> 00:39:40,490
Silly child.

970
00:39:42,410 --> 00:39:42,970
If I can earn,

971
00:39:43,222 --> 00:39:43,890
