972
00:39:45,333 --> 00:39:46,200
Don't worry about it.

973
00:39:46,266 --> 00:39:48,810
You can go out with your fishing buddies
and go out for a meal.

974
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:51,600
Stop thinking about death.

975
00:39:52,022 --> 00:39:53,488
Being alive is such a blessing.

976
00:40:04,266 --> 00:40:06,222
I looked over
your presentation slides yesterday.

977
00:40:06,222 --> 00:40:08,311
There are still a few areas
that could be improved.

978
00:40:08,333 --> 00:40:10,330
I'll be direct. The template
should be changed.

979
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:12,530
And maybe the font too.

980
00:40:14,133 --> 00:40:14,930
Hey, Lina.

981
00:40:16,155 --> 00:40:17,090
You can work on it now.

982
00:40:22,222 --> 00:40:23,010
Have a seat, Lina.

983
00:40:25,733 --> 00:40:26,530
What's the matter?

984
00:40:26,530 --> 00:40:28,000
Why are you in such a rush
to see me?

985
00:40:28,066 --> 00:40:28,933
Don't even ask.

986
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:31,200
Headmaster Zhang called me last night.

987
00:40:31,244 --> 00:40:34,044
He said the design was too similar
to Ansheng High School's uniform

988
00:40:34,044 --> 00:40:35,488
and requested to change the design.

989
00:40:35,680 --> 00:40:36,720
I'm at my wit's end.

990
00:40:36,822 --> 00:40:39,422
I have to hire a professional designer
to help him now.

991
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:41,600
They paid so little,

992
00:40:41,640 --> 00:40:43,088
yet they're still being this picky?

993
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:45,680
I don't have time

994
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:46,890
to argue about this anymore.

995
00:40:46,955 --> 00:40:48,733
The factory is waiting
to start production.

996
00:40:48,755 --> 00:40:49,733
I'm going crazy here.

997
00:40:49,755 --> 00:40:51,266
I have to get this design draft done

998
00:40:51,288 --> 00:40:52,600
and delivered in two days.

999
00:40:52,930 --> 00:40:54,680
Okay, what do you need me to do?

1000
00:40:55,970 --> 00:40:57,120
Can you help me withdraw

1001
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:59,450
