1002
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:01,240
Okay.

1003
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:03,080
No problem.

1004
00:41:04,410 --> 00:41:05,120
That's great.

1005
00:41:05,890 --> 00:41:06,890
Calm down, Lina.

1006
00:41:08,050 --> 00:41:08,410
Here.

1007
00:41:09,311 --> 00:41:09,970
Have some water.

1008
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:10,680
Thanks.

1009
00:41:10,755 --> 00:41:11,490
You're welcome.

1010
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:18,280
Lina,

1011
00:41:18,533 --> 00:41:20,330
