that much?

1012
00:41:21,111 --> 00:41:22,111
That's not the reason.

1013
00:41:22,600 --> 00:41:23,280
Well,

1014
00:41:23,970 --> 00:41:27,240
I want to help my dad buy a burial plot.

1015
