1040
00:42:33,422 --> 00:42:34,200
All right, Lina.

1041
00:42:34,200 --> 00:42:35,160
Stop worrying about it.

1042
00:42:35,422 --> 00:42:36,600
I just got my commission.

1043
00:42:36,688 --> 00:42:37,530
I can lend it to you.

1044
00:42:37,755 --> 00:42:38,490
No, it's okay.

1045
00:42:38,490 --> 00:42:39,659
Give me your account number.

1046
00:42:39,660 --> 00:42:41,190
