- Oh, it's okay.

1047
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:43,120
Young people
like you have high commitments.

1048
00:42:43,640 --> 00:42:44,200
It's okay.

1049
00:42:44,720 --> 00:42:45,970
I'll think of another way.

1050
00:42:47,044 --> 00:42:48,888
Lina, don't be embarrassed about this.

1051
00:42:51,200 --> 00:42:52,120
What if

1052
00:42:52,490 --> 00:42:54,640
I use the business loan
to invest in Joy Academy,

1053
00:42:55,370 --> 00:42:57,600
